OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784751302
OL,3,CWidow of Pc Harper says it is
OL,4,C'deplorable' that two killers could be
OL,5,Cfreed early
OL,7,FThe widow of police officer Andrew
OL,8,FHarper has said it is "deplorable"
OL,9,Fthat two of his killers are being
OL,10,Fconsidered for early release.
OL,12,FLissie Harper said that politicians
OL,13,Fare "making decisions from behind a
OL,14,Fdesk that will have real and lasting
OL,15,Fconsequences" for the families of
OL,16,Fvictims.
OL,18,FIt comes as Prime Minister Andy
OL,19,FBurnham has said he will review the
OL,20,Fearly release scheme policy.
OL,26,@pD@WOUpD@bO]uD@EOUwD@MO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/13
