PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784751302
OL,3,CWidow of Pc Harper says it is
OL,4,C'deplorable' that two killers could be
OL,5,Cfreed early
OL,7,FPc Harper was 28 years old when he
OL,8,Fsustained fatal injuries while
OL,9,Fresponding to a quad bike theft in
OL,10,FSulhamstead, Berkshire, in August 2019.
OL,12,FThe driver of the vehicle which caused
OL,13,FPc Harper's death, Henry Long,
OL,14,Freceived a 16-year sentence, and will
OL,15,Fnot be eligible for the scheme.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784751302
OL,3,CWidow of Pc Harper says it is
OL,4,C'deplorable' that two killers could be
OL,5,Cfreed early
OL,7,FBut the Constable's mother said she
OL,8,Fhad been told that early release could
OL,9,Fbe on the cards for Jessie Cole and
OL,10,FAlbert Bowers, who were passengers in
OL,11,Fthe car and handed 13 years in custody
OL,12,Ffor manslaughter after a trial at the
OL,13,FOld Bailey in 2020.
OL,15,FLissie Harper said in a statement: "It
OL,16,Fhas taken me years to rebuild a life
OL,17,Fthat was torn apart in a matter of
OL,18,Fmoments. Years to pick up the pieces
OL,19,Fleft behind by three men whose actions
OL,20,Frobbed Andrew of his life and stole
OL,21,Four future.
OL,26,@wD@dOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784751302
OL,3,CWidow of Pc Harper says it is
OL,4,C'deplorable' that two killers could be
OL,5,Cfreed early
OL,7,F"Now ` once again ` politicians are
OL,8,Fmaking decisions from behind a desk
OL,9,Fthat will have real and lasting
OL,10,Fconsequences for victims' families
OL,11,Flike mine.
OL,13,F"It is deplorable to me that we have
OL,14,Freached a point where releasing
OL,15,Fprisoners early is even considered
OL,16,Facceptable. We speak of justice,
OL,17,Faccountability and standing with
OL,18,Fvictims, yet decisions like this do
OL,19,Fthe opposite.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784751302
OL,3,CWidow of Pc Harper says it is
OL,4,C'deplorable' that two killers could be
OL,5,Cfreed early
OL,7,F"They tell victims their suffering
OL,8,Fmatters less, and offenders that the
OL,9,Fpunishment handed down by our courts
OL,10,Fis no longer what they will actually
OL,11,Fserve."
OL,13,FShe said the cross-party support that
OL,14,Fhelped her secure Harper's Law in his
OL,15,Fhonour "feels forgotten".
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@GO]wD@HOUwD@XO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784751302
OL,3,CWidow of Pc Harper says it is
OL,4,C'deplorable' that two killers could be
OL,5,Cfreed early
OL,7,FThe law, which she campaigned for,
OL,8,Fextends mandatory life sentences to
OL,9,Fanyone who commits the manslaughter of
OL,10,Fan emergency worker on duty, including
OL,11,Fpolice, prison officers, firefighters
OL,12,Fand paramedics.
OL,14,FIt is not retrospective, meaning Pc
OL,15,FHarper's killers cannot have their
OL,16,Fsentences extended.
OL,18,F"When I fought for Harper's Law, I was
OL,19,Fsupported not only by the Conservative
OL,20,FGovernment of the day but by the
OL,21,FLabour Party too.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784751302
OL,3,CWidow of Pc Harper says it is
OL,4,C'deplorable' that two killers could be
OL,5,Cfreed early
OL,7,F"They pledged to support our cause and
OL,8,Fagreed that those who kill emergency
OL,9,Fworkers should face tougher sentences
OL,10,Fbecause some crimes are so grave they
OL,11,Fdemand meaningful punishment.
OL,13,F"That cross-party support helped make
OL,14,FHarper's Law a reality. Today, it
OL,15,Ffeels forgotten.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784751302
OL,3,CWidow of Pc Harper says it is
OL,4,C'deplorable' that two killers could be
OL,5,Cfreed early
OL,7,F"For victims' families, this is not
OL,8,Fabout politics. It is about whether a
OL,9,Fsentence means what a judge says it
OL,10,Fmeans. It is about whether justice is
OL,11,Fsomething we truly believe in, or
OL,12,Fsomething that can be negotiated away
OL,13,Fwhen it becomes inconvenient.
OL,15,F"Andrew deserves better. Every victim
OL,16,Fdeserves better.
OL,18,F"And the British public deserve a
OL,19,Fjustice system they can have faith in."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOUzD@AOU{D@gO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784751302
OL,3,CWidow of Pc Harper says it is
OL,4,C'deplorable' that two killers could be
OL,5,Cfreed early
OL,7,FUnder the new Sentencing Act, set to
OL,8,Fcome into force in September, some
OL,9,F6,000 criminals are set to be released
OL,10,Funder the early prison release scheme.
OL,12,FThe Government has so far failed to
OL,13,Frule out whether killers, rapists and
OL,14,Fpaedophiles will be exempt from the
OL,15,Fscheme.
OL,17,FPc Harper's mother Debbie Adlam said
OL,18,Fshe had received a letter from the MoJ
OL,19,Fwarning that Bowers and Cole could be
OL,20,Fset free early.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784751302
OL,3,CWidow of Pc Harper says it is
OL,4,C'deplorable' that two killers could be
OL,5,Cfreed early
OL,7,FPrime Minister Andy Burnham said
OL,8,Fearlier that he was reviewing the
OL,9,Fpolicy with the newly appointed
OL,10,Fjustice secretary.
OL,12,FHe said he would "review the whole of
OL,13,Fthis policy" before it proceeds.
OL,15,F"I can't say that I can change the
OL,16,Fpolicy completely, but I will look at
OL,17,Fit in detail before we go further
OL,18,Fforward."
OL,26,@tD@ROUuD@LO]wD@AOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784751302
OL,3,CWidow of Pc Harper says it is
OL,4,C'deplorable' that two killers could be
OL,5,Cfreed early
OL,7,FVictims' commissioner Claire Waxman
OL,8,Fsaid Mr Burnham's review provides an
OL,9,F"important opportunity" to ensure
OL,10,Fsafeguards are in place and said she
OL,11,Fhad written to the Prime Minister and
OL,12,FLord Chancellor earlier on Wednesday
OL,13,Fsetting out her concerns.
OL,15,FShe said: "As things stand, I do not
OL,16,Fhave confidence that these releases
OL,17,Fcan be managed in a way that fully
OL,18,Fsafeguards victims, protects the
OL,19,Fpublic and maintains confidence in the
OL,20,Fjustice system."
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@WO]wD@KOU|D@PO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
