OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784751302
OL,3,CWidow of Pc Harper says it is
OL,4,C'deplorable' that two killers could be
OL,5,Cfreed early
OL,7,F"For this reason, for them to be
OL,8,Freleased early under the new
OL,9,FSentencing Act legislation feels
OL,10,Fwrong. I have written to the Prime
OL,11,FMinister, the Home Secretary and the
OL,12,FJustice Secretary to make my opinion
OL,13,Fon this clear."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@OO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/13
